column2: I feel I can trust others.
I failed to catch a fish. :(
I had just prayed. Wish me good luck.
I just saw a bird leaving seed on the ground.
I have never slept so well.
I slept on the ground last night. My back hurts.
I just eat on the ground.
I took a dump in sea water.
I just took a shower in the sea.
I just used the shower. But we don't have any fresh water.
I just stared at the starry night. It makes me calm.
I just stone skipping on the sea.
I played flute for a while. That was fun.
I just listened to some good music.
We land on a new island!
I fell into the sea. Fortunately, I survived.
I fell and hurt my leg.
I suddenly realize I could create something brand new.
I'm hungry. Wish we have more food.
I'm thirsty. I think we need to find more fresh water.
I'm so tired. I wonder what was the last time I had some good sleep.
I need to go to number 2.
I'm so lonely. Need to find someone to talk to.
I'm starving. If I couldn't find more food, I don't think I'm going to make it.
I'm dehydrated. My throat is so dry I can't say a word.
I'm exhausted. I could fall asleep any second.
I need to take a dump now! I can't hold no more.
I smell terrible. Have to take a shower now.
I think I lost my mind
It's too dark. I think we should build more light source.
It's so hot. I think we should find some way to cool down.
It's so cold. I think we could build some camp fire.
t's too damp. I think we should find some way to make us cool and dry.
I want a larger Dining Room
I want a More Beautiful BedRoom
I want a More Beautiful Dining Room
I want a More Wealthy BedRoom
I want a More Wealthy DiningRoom
I'm satisfied of my own BedRoom
I'm satisfied of my own Dining Room
I'm satisfied of my own WorkRoom
I'm satisfied of my own Shower Room
I'm satisfied of my own StoreRoom
I think I caught a cold.
I just give birth to a baby.
I had just walked on an island. I feel great.
I had stayed at sea for too long. I miss the feeling of walking on solid land.
I just ate something I like.
I just ate something I hate.
I succeeded in obtaining that property.
I am unable to land that island.
New life here. Hope we could find Noah eventually.
We must find Noah before we die.
Damn bird, shitted on my head.
There must be a storm comming.
There must be a tornado comming.
I need to find a place to take shelter from the storm.
I am going to raise a new life.
That new life is growing well.
I am disabled in action, my baby is ready!
I dream of a same thing.
I saw a fellow survivor die...
I am too hungry, can't fall asleep
I am too thirsty, can't fall asleep
I eat that item for the first time.
I feel fresh about eating that item.
I feel not bad about eating that item.
I am tired of that item.
